"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, the target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"foci in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the target is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method has no effect if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userTrackingMode"},{"type":"text","text":" property is set to a value"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other than "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To specify a completion handler to execute after the animation finishes, use","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the ","type":"text"},{"code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/settargetcoordinate:animated:"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Deprecated. Sets the geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the user location is being tracked, with an optional transition animation.","type":"text"}],"kind":"s